{"type": "article", "id": 29639, "title": "旋转的日历", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-14T23:02:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 85, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160714231137bNlxZ8PKqen3Todi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>如果你依然对纸质挂历感兴趣而且喜欢动手，<a href=\"http://taitdesignco.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tait Design</a> 公司最近推出的 Perpetual Calendar 或许会让你眼前一亮。以旧时的潮汐仪为灵感设计的挂历使用起来非常有趣，只要轻轻转动挂历上三个圆形卡纸，日期就会发生相应的变化。正因为这种简朴的设计，它也不会和其他挂历一样每一年都需要换新，能够一年年重复使用，无论是放在办公室还是家中都很合适。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/perpetual-calendar-tait-design-06-24-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 50 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142311588CWOfjXwNAHel0gR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016071423115907L5e4rH1nMudmRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160714231159Y8nkzoPm3RMvuC4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607142311596s5F7SnX8AqTCt4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}